We might also see Carvajal and/or Marcelo being rested before the crucial game against Atletico in the Champions League. Starting lineup will probably looks something like this : Navas, Carvajal/Arbeloa, Marcelo/Coentrao, Ramos, Varane, Isco, Modric, Illara/L.Silva, Bale, Benzema, Jese. This match with all the players missing has the potential to become really complicated. Eibar is on a poor run of form but it won't be as easy as some might think.
